    "anime_effect_en": "You can Ritual Summon this card with \"Machine Angel Ritual\". When this card is targeted for an attack while you control another \"Cyber\" monster: You can negate the attack. Once per turn: You can target 1 face-up monster you control; gain LP equal to half its ATK. If this card is in your Graveyard: You can banish 1 other \"Cyber Angel\" monster from your Graveyard, then target 1 monster your opponent controls; Special Summon this card, and if you do, take control of that target.",
