    "anime_effect_en": "Activate this card by targeting 1 monster your opponent controls that was Special Summoned from the Extra Deck. When this card is activated: You can Special Summon 2 \"Keeper Shield Tokens\" (Warrior-Type/LIGHT/Level 1/ATK 0/DEF 0). The targeted monster's effects are negated, also it can attack all \"Keeper Shield Tokens\" once each. If the targeted monster did not attack all \"Keeper Shield Tokens\" during the Battle Phase, destroy it at the end of the Battle Phase. If the targeted monster leaves the field, destroy this card.",
